 {"id":"bd-nzv3.14","title":"btrfs send/receive: extract protocol model and supported workflow contract","description":"Define the send/receive surface precisely: stream record model, ordering rules, snapshot assumptions, xattr/metadata coverage, error handling, and the minimum viable user workflow that FrankenFS will support first.","acceptance_criteria":"Closure requires: implementation-ready protocol model, explicit first-version scope boundaries, crate/module ownership plan, user-visible send and receive workflow contract, and spec/parity updates that describe the supported workflow without hand-waving.","notes":"Also enumerate the verification plan: send-only stream correctness, receive apply correctness, roundtrip expectations, rejected record classes, CLI/operator workflow expectations, and logging/diagnostics for export/apply failures.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-23T01:06:25.619924719Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-23T06:15:44.576942469Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["btrfs","send-receive","spec"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-nzv3.14","depends_on_id":"bd-nzv3","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-23T01:06:25.619924719Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-nzv3.15","title":"btrfs send/receive: implement deterministic send stream export","description":"Implement the scoped send side from bd-nzv3.14 so supported snapshots can be exported into deterministic streams with explicit handling for unsupported operations or metadata classes.","acceptance_criteria":"Closure requires: deterministic stream emission tests, integration coverage over representative snapshots, and structured diagnostics for omitted or rejected operations.","notes":"Do not call this complete until the produced stream format is stable enough for the receive bead to consume under tests.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-03-23T01:06:26.762330403Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-23T06:16:07.630629952Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["btrfs","implementation","qa_e2e_required","qa_structured_logging_required","qa_unit_required","send-receive"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-nzv3.15","depends_on_id":"bd-nzv3","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-23T01:06:26.762330403Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-nzv3.15","depends_on_id":"bd-nzv3.14","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-23T06:11:30.219190839Z","created_by":"PearlFox","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-nzv3.15","depends_on_id":"bd-nzv3.25","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-23T06:16:07.629918665Z","created_by":"PearlFox","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
