 {"id":"bd-nzv3.16","title":"btrfs send/receive: implement receive apply path, roundtrip tests, and e2e logging","description":"Implement receive-side apply semantics for the scoped protocol and verify the user workflow end-to-end. This bead turns send/receive into an actual parity feature rather than a one-way export primitive.","acceptance_criteria":"Closure requires: deterministic receive tests, send→receive roundtrip coverage, explicit rejection tests for unsupported stream content, and at least one detailed e2e script that logs stream generation, apply, and verification results.","notes":"Parity/docs updates must say exactly what stream features and filesystem mutations are supported after closure.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-23T01:06:27.925148046Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-23T06:16:08.813652943Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["btrfs","qa_e2e_required","qa_structured_logging_required","qa_unit_required","send-receive","tests"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-nzv3.16","depends_on_id":"bd-nzv3","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-23T01:06:27.925148046Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-nzv3.16","depends_on_id":"bd-nzv3.15","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-23T06:11:31.410713157Z","created_by":"PearlFox","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-nzv3.16","depends_on_id":"bd-nzv3.25","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-23T06:16:08.812906380Z","created_by":"PearlFox","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
